&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Please note that travel to Gusto&#39;s Denver office for onboarding is required for this position.&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;If you have any questions regarding this requirement, please share with your recruiter.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Our cash compensation amount for this role is targeted at $191,000-$225,000 in Denver &amp;amp; most remote locations, and $225,000-$265,000 in San Francisco and New York. Final offer amounts are determined by multiple factors including candidate experience and expertise and may vary from the amounts listed above.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;content-conclusion&quot;&gt;&lt;hr&gt;
